going to go or an index.

00:50:20.940 --> 00:50:24.054
You never know how long
an index is going to go.

00:50:24.054 --> 00:50:25.970
So this is an important
background information

00:50:25.970 --> 00:50:28.300
because if you're thinking
of buying a company's stock,

00:50:28.300 --> 00:50:31.630
75% of stocks are going to
