01:02:47.130 --> 01:02:51.565
going to pay live worth
plus 100 basis points.

01:02:51.565 --> 01:02:55.190
And the lender is going to
put a lien on the assets.

01:02:55.190 --> 01:02:59.760
That doesn't happen in
the enterprising mindset.

01:02:59.760 --> 01:03:01.670
So there are two
different mindsets here.

